The paper discusses the formalization of concepts in the Security Assessment domain, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The use of ontologies also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and the paper discusses research issues and application domains, which are relevant to software engineering (cs.SE) and databases (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of machine learning techniques (cs.LG) in some of the surveyed works.
